@page "/eurojackpot"

<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.Medium" Class="pa-4">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" GutterBottom="true">What is Euro Jackpot?</MudText>
    <MudDivider Class="mb-3" />

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        <b>Euro Jackpot</b> is one of the largest transnational lottery games in Europe. It offers huge jackpots and multiple ways to win, with draws held every Friday.
        The lottery follows a specific number sequence format, which is important to understand if you wish to participate or use a tool like <b>JackpotOracle</b> to predict numbers.
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">How Does Euro Jackpot Work?</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        Players must choose a combination of numbers from two separate pools:
    </MudText>

    <MudList Class="mb-3" T="string">
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1"><b>Main Numbers:</b> Choose 5 unique numbers from a pool of numbers between 1 and 50.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1"><b>Euro Numbers:</b> Choose 2 unique numbers from a separate pool of numbers between 1 and 12.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
    </MudList>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Winning the Jackpot</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        To win the jackpot, you need to match:
    </MudText>
    <MudList Class="mb-3" T="string">
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ All 5 main numbers.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Both Euro numbers.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
    </MudList>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Other Prize Tiers</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        In addition to the jackpot, Euro Jackpot offers several prize tiers based on how many numbers you match.
        Here are the possible combinations:
    </MudText>

    <MudList Class="mb-3" T="string">
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Match 5 main numbers + 2 Euro numbers: Jackpot.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Match 5 main numbers + 1 Euro number: Lower-tier prize.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Match 5 main numbers: Even lower-tier prize.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Match 4 main numbers + 2 Euro numbers: Mid-tier prize.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Match 4 main numbers + 1 Euro number: Smaller prize.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
        <MudListItem>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">✔ Match 3 main numbers + 2 Euro numbers: Smaller prize.</MudText>
        </MudListItem>
    </MudList>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Example Draw Sequence</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        Here’s an example of a typical Euro Jackpot draw:
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        <b>Main Numbers:</b> 5, 12, 23, 38, 46<br />
        <b>Euro Numbers:</b> 3, 7
    </MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true">
        In this example, a player who selected <b>5, 12, 23, 38, 46</b> as their main numbers and <b>3, 7</b> as their Euro numbers would win the jackpot.
    </MudText>

    <MudDivider Class="mt-3 mb-3" />

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
        <b>Disclaimer:</b> Euro Jackpot is a game of chance, and while predictions can help, there is no guarantee of winning.
    </MudText>
</MudContainer>
